  "system": {
    "description": "<p>A sword that is connected with a wire that runs through various links that make up the sword, which can be retracted and extended at will. A character may switch a whip sword&rsquo;s form for 1 CP. Whip swords come with a tactical sheath.</p>\n<p><strong>Sword Form:</strong> When the whip sword is in this mode, it is considered a shortsword and gains any benefits that a shortsword would gain from feats and abilities.</p>\n<p><strong>Whip Form:</strong> When a whip sword is in this mode, it is considered a bullwhip and gains any benefits that a bullwhip would gain from feats and abilities.</p>",
